'''二(4-甲苯磺酰亚氨基)硒'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为C<sub>14</sub>H<sub>14</sub>N<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>S<sub>2</sub>Se。它可由[[氯胺T|氯胺T]]和[[硒|硒]]在[[二氯甲烷|二氯甲烷]]中反应，或由''N'',''N''-二(三甲基硅基)-4-甲苯磺酰胺和[[二氯氧化硒|二氯氧化硒]]反应得到。<ref name=Se>{{cite book|location=Chichester, UK|language=en|isbn=9780471936237|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|date=2001-04-15|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/047084289X.rb193|title=Bis[ N -( p -toluenesulfonyl)]selenodiimide|accessdate=2020-11-28|editor= John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|author=Steven M. Weinreb, Geoffrey R. Heintzelman|doi=10.1002/047084289x.rb193}}</ref>它和[[三乙胺盐酸盐|三乙胺盐酸盐]]反应，生成二(4-甲苯磺酰胺基)二氯化硒<!-- (BzNH)2SeCl2 -->。<ref>Barashenkov, G. G.; Derkach, N. Ya. ''Zhurnal Organicheskoi Khimii'', 1986. 22 (6): 1189-1195. ISSN: 0514-7492.</ref>它和3-丁烯-1,2-二胺反应，生成3-乙烯基-1,2,5-硒二唑。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthesis|volume=1979|issue=12|language=en|issn=0039-7881|date=1979|pages=979–980|doi=10.1055/s-1979-28899|url=http://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055/s-1979-28899|title=3-Vinyl-1,2,5-selenadiazole|accessdate=2020-11-28|author=Vincenzo Bertini, Francesco Lucchesini, Angela De Munno|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602013238/https://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055%2Fs-1979-28899|dead-url=no}}</ref>

